These are the files I have coded so far for a wordpress theme satisfying the following requirements:
- mobile-friendly and mobile-responsive
- different content displayed for desktop and mobile users
- fully compatible with plugins from the wordpress ecosystem
- compatible with popular SEO plugins like yoast
- fixed header but not fixed footer for each page
- a menu is in the header, with menu items and sub-items. Each of the menu items and sub-items change cover when the user hovers over the text. Each menu item links to a separate page (to be customized later).
- CSS functionality replaces JavaScript whenever possible
- Use ARIA roles and labels where necessary.
- Ensure sufficient color contrast, especially for hover states and interactive elements.
- Always use wp_enqueue_style to load styles conditionally  
- Ensure that if CSS fails to load, the website remains functional 
- For menus, ensure that they are accessible without JavaScript 

Check my code for mistakes, misplaced code blocks, and failure to satisfying any of the above requirements.

---

FILE: style.css

```css

/*
Theme Name: Custom Landing Page
Theme URI: http://example.com/
Author: Your Name
Author URI: http://example.com/
Description: A custom landing page theme.
Version: 1.1
License: GNU General Public License v2 or later
License URI: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html
Text Domain: custom-landing-page
*/

/* Reset some default styles */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

header {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  z-index: 1000; /* Ensures the header stays above other elements */
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  background-color: #0044cc;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Optional: Adds a subtle shadow */
}

body {
  padding-top: 70px; /* Adjust based on header height */
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  color: #333;
}

header img.logo {
  height: 50px;
  margin-right: 20px;
}

.menu-toggle-checkbox {
  display: none;
}

.menu-toggle-label {
  display: none;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.menu {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.menu-ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.menu-item {
  position: relative;
}

.menu-item a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  border-radius: 3px;
}

.menu-item a:hover {
  color: #ffcc00;
  background-color: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.2);
}

.menu-item-has-children .sub-menu {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  top: 100%;
  left: 0;
  background-color: #0044cc;
  padding: 10px 0;
  list-style: none;
  min-width: 150px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  z-index: 1000;
}

.menu-item-has-children:hover .sub-menu {
  display: block;
}

.sub-menu li {
  margin: 5px 0;
}

.sub-menu a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s, background-color 0.3s;
  display: block;
  padding: 5px 20px;
}

.sub-menu a:hover {
  color: #ffcc00;
  background-color: rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.2);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .menu {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #0044cc;
    padding: 10px;
    position: absolute;
    top: 60px; /* Adjust based on header height */
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .menu-ul {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .menu-toggle-label {
    display: block;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .menu-toggle-checkbox:checked + .menu-toggle-label + .menu {
    display: flex;
  }

  .menu-item-has-children .sub-menu {
    position: static;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

  .menu-item-has-children:hover .sub-menu {
    display: none; /* Disable hover on mobile */
  }

  .menu-item-has-children .sub-menu {
    display: none;
  }

  .menu-item-has-children:focus-within .sub-menu,
  .menu-item-has-children .sub-menu:hover {
    display: block;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .mobile-only {
    display: block;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 769px) {
  .mobile-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: block;
  }
}

.content-area {
  padding: 20px;
}

footer {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 20px 10px;
  position: relative;
  /* No fixed positioning as per requirements */
}

.footer-content a {
  color: #ffcc00;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s;
}

.footer-content a:hover {
  color: #ffffff;
}

/* Additional Styling for Accessibility and Enhancements */

/* Focus States for Accessibility */
.menu-item a:focus,
.sub-menu a:focus {
  outline: 2px dashed #ffcc00;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}

/* Smooth Transition for Menu Toggle */
.menu {
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease-in-out;
}


